[03/04/2019 13:34:14] <font color="#ffffff">Hola, Danny.</font>
[03/04/2019 13:34:14] <font color="#ffffff">-Hola, Bob.</font>
[03/04/2019 13:34:15] <font color="#ffffff">-Hola, Danny.</font>
